flowRoot.flowPara: Each Inkscape layer will become the output context. Icons are composed of a group that contains a 16x16px rectangle object. Duplicate it and enter the group with to edit.
As the bounding box is set to no-stroke, no-fill you will find it useful to work in outline view mode.
To name an icon, use Object Properties and set its title. Label attribute holds space separated keywords used for search. Color of the icon doesn't matter as all of them recolor at run time.
